TITLE: Ruby Selenium WebDriver Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Ruby implementation of the Google search test scenario using Selenium WebDriver and Cucumber step definitions
SOURCE: https://github.com/cucumber/docs/blob/main/content/docs/guides/browser-automation.md#2025-04-09_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: ruby
CODE:
```
require 'rubygems'
require 'selenium-webdriver'

Given(/^I am on the Google search page$/) do
  driver = Selenium::WebDriver.for :firefox
  driver.get "http://google.com"
end

When(/^I search for "([^"]*)"$/) do
  element = driver.find_element(name: "q")
