TITLE: Advanced Database Cleaning Configuration in Ruby
DESCRIPTION: Comprehensive setup for Database Cleaner in Ruby that uses transactions by default but switches to truncation for scenarios tagged with @no-txn. It handles proper cleaning before and after each scenario.
