TITLE: Database Cleaning with DatabaseCleaner in Ruby
DESCRIPTION: Sets up Database Cleaner to clean the database before scenarios tagged with @no-txn. It uses truncation strategy to ensure a clean database state before each tagged scenario.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cucumber/docs/blob/main/content/docs/cucumber/state.md#2025-04-09_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: ruby
CODE:
```
require 'database_cleaner'
DatabaseCleaner.clean_with :truncation # clean once to ensure clean slate
DatabaseCleaner.strategy = :truncation

Before('@no-txn') do
  DatabaseCleaner.start
end

After('@no-txn') do
  DatabaseCleaner.clean
end
```

